titleStmt.title: A panegyrick on Her Most Excellent Majestie, Katharine, Queen of England, Scotland, France, and Ireland, or, Her Highness cordiall welcome into England Her Royal Majesty landed at Portsmouth, on Wednesday night, the 14 this instant May, to the great joy of all those that truly fear God, and honour the King / by Lancelot Reynolds, Gent.
titleStmt.author: Reynolds, Lancelot.
